column5: I was going through files on my computer and deleting stuff that I didnt need (it's been very slow lately).  I came across a video file entitled stevebass.wmv  I didnt remember it, but it sounded right.  When I clicked on it, it was a whole bunched of video footage that I shot when I was 17.  It was kind of funny watching myself back then, I do things so much differently now.  There were even a couple "set up" shots that I had a good laugh at.  I thought I'd throw some of the clips together (without sound) and share them. Laugh if you want, I did.
in my original post it says (without sound) Brian.
